params.to: address to be approved for the given token ID
params.tokenId: uint256 ID of the token to be approved

params.owner: address to query the balance of

params._allotments: an array of arrays of points for creating the allotment bounds Each lat lng point has six decimal points, about 4 inches of precision. (precision is not accuracy, note https://gis.stackexchange.com/a/8674 )

params._price: uint of the cost (in ecoBucks) of the new microaddon
params._purchasable: bool determining if the new microaddon can be purchased by users

params.tokenId: uint256 ID of the token to query the approval of
